= Taiwan Sample Client Plugin =

'''Taiwan Sample Client Plugin''' (tw.idempiere.sample) is an OSGi plugin that creates a complete Taiwan demo company with localized Chart of Accounts, sample products, business partners, and tax settings.

== Overview ==

This plugin solves common challenges for Taiwan iDempiere users:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Challenge !! Solution
|-
| Default US GAAP Chart of Accounts || Taiwan Commercial Accounting Law compliant accounts (111 accounts)
|-
| No Chinese sample data || Complete demo company "天地人實業有限公司" (Tian Di Ren Enterprise Co., Ltd.)
|-
| Time-consuming initial setup || One-click setup for organizations, warehouses, products, and business partners
|}

== Features ==

=== Organizations (3) ===
* '''台北總公司''' (Taipei HQ) - Main headquarters
* '''台中分公司''' (Taichung Branch) - Central region operations
* '''高雄倉庫''' (Kaohsiung Warehouse) - Southern logistics center

=== Warehouses (4) ===
* Taipei Main Warehouse
* Taipei Store Warehouse
* Taichung Warehouse
* Kaohsiung Warehouse

=== Taiwan Chart of Accounts (111 accounts) ===

The plugin imports a complete Taiwan-standard Chart of Accounts with proper tree hierarchy:

<pre>
1 Assets (資產)
├── 11 Current Assets (流動資產)
│   ├── 111 Cash and Cash Equivalents (現金及約當現金)
│   ├── 112 Short-term Investments (短期投資)
│   ├── 113 Notes Receivable (應收票據)
│   ├── 114 Accounts Receivable (應收帳款)
│   └── 119 Inventory (存貨)
├── 12 Non-current Assets (非流動資產)
2 Liabilities (負債)
├── 21 Current Liabilities (流動負債)
3 Equity (權益)
4 Operating Revenue (營業收入)
5 Operating Costs (營業成本)
6 Operating Expenses (營業費用)
7 Non-operating Income/Expenses (營業外收支)
8 Income Tax Expense (所得稅費用)
</pre>

=== Tax Settings (3) ===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Tax Name !! Rate !! Usage
|-
| 應稅 5% (Taxable) || 5% || Standard goods/services
|-
| 零稅率 (Zero-rated) || 0% || Export goods
|-
| 免稅 (Exempt) || 0% || Tax-exempt goods
|}

=== Price Lists (3) ===
* Standard Sales Price List
* Standard Purchase Price List
* Employee Price List

=== Products (31) ===
Sample products across categories:
* Paper products (A4 paper, envelopes)
* Writing supplies (pens, pencils)
* Office supplies (staplers, scissors)
* Filing supplies (folders, binders)
* Electronics (USB drives, mouse, keyboard)
* Services (consulting, maintenance)

=== Business Partners (18) ===
* 10 Customers
* 5 Vendors
* 3 Employees

