== Installation ==

=== Download ===

Download the JAR from GitHub Releases:
* https://github.com/tm731531/idempiere-tw-init-tenant/releases

=== Install via OSGi Console ===

'''Option A: Web Console'''
# Open browser: <code>http://your-server:8080/osgi/system/console/bundles</code>
# Login (default: admin/admin)
# Click "Install/Update"
# Select the JAR file
# Check "Start"
# Click "Install or Update"

'''Option B: Telnet/SSH'''
<syntaxhighlight lang="bash">
telnet localhost 12612

# Install and start
install file:/opt/idempiere/plugins/tw.idempiere.sample-2.0.0.jar
start <bundle-id>
</syntaxhighlight>

=== Verify Installation ===

<syntaxhighlight lang="bash">
# In OSGi Console
lb | grep -i taiwan
# Should show: Active | tw.idempiere.sample
</syntaxhighlight>

== Post-Installation ==

After the plugin starts, it automatically creates:
# Client "天地人實業有限公司"
# 3 Organizations
# 4 Warehouses
# 111 Taiwan Chart of Accounts (with tree hierarchy)
# Tax settings
# 3 Price Lists
# 31 Products
# 18 Business Partners

